                "html": "<div style=\"padding:20px 24px;border-right:1px solid rgba(155,142,196,.25);\"><div style=\"font-size:28px;margin-bottom:10px;\">&#127807;</div><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond,serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:400;color:#1e2a1f;margin-bottom:6px;\">Profumo di Elicriso</h4><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.65;color:#7a7068;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;\">L&apos;oro di Sardegna fiorisce intorno al tuo domo. Un&apos;aromaterapia naturale senza uguale.</p></div>"
