                "html": "<div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px;margin-top:28px;\"><div style=\"border-left:2px solid #c9a84c;padding:10px 0 10px 16px;\"><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond,serif;font-size:17px;color:#c9a84c;margin-bottom:5px;\">Letto King Size</h4><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(253,252,250,0.5);line-height:1.6;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;\">Biancheria artigianale sarda, materasso premium, cuscini in piuma d&apos;oca</p></div><div style=\"border-left:2px solid #c9a84c;padding:10px 0 10px 16px;\"><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond,serif;font-size:17px;color:#c9a84c;margin-bottom:5px;\">Bagno Privato Esterno</h4><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(253,252,250,0.5);line-height:1.6;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;\">Doccia a cielo aperto, prodotti biologici locali all&apos;elicriso</p></div><div style=\"border-left:2px solid #c9a84c;padding:10px 0 10px 16px;\"><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond,serif;font-size:17px;color:#c9a84c;margin-bottom:5px;\">Cupola Trasparente</h4><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(253,252,250,0.5);line-height:1.6;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;\">Finestra zenitale apribile per dormire sotto le stelle della Gallura</p></div><div style=\"border-left:2px solid #c9a84c;padding:10px 0 10px 16px;\"><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond,serif;font-size:17px;color:#c9a84c;margin-bottom:5px;\">Terrazza Privata</h4><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(253,252,250,0.5);line-height:1.6;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;\">Hamaca, tavolo per due e braciere. Vista sul bosco di lecci</p></div><div style=\"border-left:2px solid #c9a84c;padding:10px 0 10px 16px;\"><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond,serif;font-size:17px;color:#c9a84c;margin-bottom:5px;\">Climatizzazione Naturale</h4><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(253,252,250,0.5);line-height:1.6;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;\">Ventilazione passiva ad alta efficienza &mdash; zero energia sprecata</p></div><div style=\"border-left:2px solid #c9a84c;padding:10px 0 10px 16px;\"><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond,serif;font-size:17px;color:#c9a84c;margin-bottom:5px;\">Design Sostenibile</h4><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(253,252,250,0.5);line-height:1.6;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;\">Legno certificato FSC, energia 100% solare, zero plastiche monouso</p></div></div>"
