            {
              "id": "cta0003",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "html",
              "settings": {
                "html": "<div style=\"max-width:760px;margin:0 auto;background:#fdfcfa;padding:70px 60px;box-shadow:0 24px 80px rgba(155,142,196,0.15);text-align:center;\">\n  <div style=\"display:inline-block;background:#c9a84c;color:#fdfcfa;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:6px 16px;margin-bottom:28px;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;\">&#10022; Offerta Fondatori &mdash; Posti Limitati</div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond,serif;font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,46px);font-weight:300;color:#1e2a1f;line-height:1.12;margin-bottom:16px;\">Sei pronto a <em style=\"font-style:italic;color:#9b8ec4;\">sentirti vivo</em> sul serio?</h2>\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;color:#7a7068;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-weight:300;max-width:520px;margin:0 auto 28px;\">I nostri domos si riempiono settimane in anticipo. Unisciti alla lista d&apos;attesa oggi e assicurati il tuo posto &mdash; con un privilegio esclusivo per chi arriva per primo.</p>\n  <div style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;background:#f5efd6;border:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.3);padding:14px 28px;margin-bottom:28px;\">\n    <span style=\"font-size:20px;\">&#127873;</span>\n    <div style=\"text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-size:16px;color:#b56344;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;\">15% di sconto</strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#3a3530;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;\"> per i primi 20 ospiti &middot; Kit aromatico di benvenuto con elicriso e lavanda di Gallura incluso</span></div>\n  </div>\n  <form style=\"display:flex;max-width:440px;margin:0 auto 14px;\" onsubmit=\"this.querySelector('button').textContent='Sei nella lista!';this.querySelector('button').style.background='#4a6442';event.preventDefault();\">\n    <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"la-tua@email.com\" required style=\"flex:1;padding:14px 18px;border:1px solid rgba(200,184,154,.6);border-right:none;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-size:15px;outline:none;color:#3a3530;background:#fff;\" />\n    <button type=\"submit\" style=\"padding:14px 24px;background:#9b8ec4;border:none;color:#fdfcfa;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap;\">Unisciti &rarr;</button>\n  </form>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7a7068;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;\">&#128274; Nessuno spam. Solo disponibilit&agrave;, offerte esclusive e storie di Gallura.</p>\n</div>"
